---
title: Honey Beef Koftas & Garlic Hummus Yoghurt with Haloumi & Roasted Cauliflower-Carrot Couscous
description: You will be floating on clouds with this beef kofta, haloumi and couscous dinner. A flavourful honey drizzle coats the koftas and will send
your tastebuds to dreamland, especially when you add a fragrant hummus and yoghurt combo.
